    "body": "Is it possible to support [uvloop](https://github.com/magicstack/uvloop)?\r\n\r\nRequirement \r\n------------------\r\nPython >= 3.5\r\nuvloop\r\nlinux only!\r\n\r\nTo make asyncio use uvloop\r\n----------------------------------------\r\n\r\n```python\r\nimport asyncio\r\nimport uvloop\r\nasyncio.set_event_loop_policy(uvloop.EventLoopPolicy())\r\n```\r\n\r\nPerformance\r\n------------------\r\n![Performance](https://github.com/MagicStack/uvloop/raw/master/performance.png)\r\n\r\n\r\nThank you.\r\n",
